thread.title: Trump meets Turnbull, mum on Rick Gates

title: Trump meets Turnbull, mum on Rick Gates
text:
Trump meets Turnbull, mum on Rick Gates 12:39am IST - 00:47 
During a meeting with Australia's Prime Minister Malcolm Turnbull, President Trump declines to respond to reporters' questions regarding his former deputy campaign manager Rick Gates who is set to plead guilty in the Russia probe. Rough Cut
